</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3E590F30FC0DA93EAAD8FB33B276AE1A" blockId="9.[189,1399,1240,1372]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
The specimen with code CASENT0906379 labelled on AntWeb as a worker specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="F9E674B3FC0DA93EAE8DFB32B65EAFB4" authorityName="Cephalic" baseAuthorityName="Hamann &amp; Klemm" baseAuthorityYear="1967" box="[1256,1398,1240,1266]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Temnothorax" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="megalops">
<emphasis id="0C92D322FC0DA93EAE8DFB32B65EAFB4" box="[1256,1398,1240,1266]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">T. megalops</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(collected from 
<collectingCountry id="46F14FA0FC0DA93EAB1BFB10B2FBAE53" box="[382,467,1275,1301]" name="Yemen" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Yemen</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion id="FC22C1D2FC0DA93EAB85FB10B119AE53" box="[480,561,1275,1301]" country="Yemen" name="Abyan" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Abyan</collectingRegion>
, Al Kawd, 
<date id="4A5829F0FC0DA93EA8D8FB10B079AE53" box="[701,849,1275,1301]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" value="2001-09-07">7 Sep. 2001</date>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="5BD269F7FC0DA93EA905FB10B0D4AE53" box="[864,1020,1275,1301]" degrees="13.08861" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" precision="1" value="13.08861">13.08861° N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="5BD269F7FC0DA93EAE6EFB10B78BAE53" box="[1035,1187,1275,1302]" degrees="45.36472" direction="east" orientation="longitude" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" precision="1" value="45.36472">45.36472° E</geoCoordinate>
, Van Harten leg., WMLC), actually represents a species of 
<taxonomicName id="F9E674B3FC0DA93EA8AEFAF4B04BAE7E" authorityName="Wheeler" authorityYear="1910" box="[715,867,1311,1336]" class="Insecta" family="Hymenoptera" genus="Nesomyrmex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="0C92D322FC0DA93EA8AEFAF4B04BAE7E" box="[715,867,1311,1336]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Nesomyrmex</emphasis>
